			<ns0:name>dsch...@google.com</ns0:name><ns0:uri>/u/104270846665912603141/</ns0:uri></ns0:author><ns0:content type="html">The PNaCl driver's Run method pushes all stdin and stdout from the subproceses around manually in a polling loop, killing the performance of tools like llvm-dis which use stdin/out rather than files for their output.

